description:
# Fixed Asset Accountss

With the company, a host of fixed asset accountss are pre-configured. To ensure your asset transactions are leading to correct accountsing entries, you can review and set up following asset accountss as per your business  requirements.
 - Fixed asset accountss (Asset accounts)
 - Accumulated depreciation
 - Capital Work in progress (CWIP) accounts
 - Asset Depreciation accounts (Expense accounts)
